# .roadmap.disease_adc

작성: 2026-05-08
구동: 사용자 directive `/loop 5m keep going` cron `34b18744` + 대량 bg batch (105-108)

본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap (modality-platform). hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 ADC (antibody-drug conjugate — antibody + linker + cytotoxic payload modality) 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + 신규 약물 기준 falsifier inventory.

(Distinct from `.roadmap.disease_cancer` (broad) + `.roadmap.disease_cell_therapy_platform` (CAR-T): ADC = antibody-drug conjugate — antibody + linker + cytotoxic payload modality. 2000 Mylotarg first FDA → 2017 re-approval + 2013 Kadcyla + 2019 Enhertu + 2019 Padcev + 2020 Trodelvy + 2024+ expansion. 양자-VQE 의 fit: antibody Fab + linker chemistry + payload binding.)

scope:
- HER2 ADC (Kadcyla T-DM1 + Enhertu T-DXd + 2024 expansion)
- TROP2 ADC (Trodelvy + datopotamab deruxtecan 2024 + 2025+)
- nectin-4 ADC (Padcev urothelial)
- CD33 ADC (Mylotarg AML — cross-bone_marrow_failure)
- CD22 ADC (Besponsa B-cell ALL)
- CD30 ADC (Adcetris HL/T-cell)
- CD79b ADC (Polivy DLBCL)
- BCMA ADC (Blenrep — withdrawn 2022 → 2024 BLENREP returns)
- 자가면역 ADC research (anti-IL-23 + 표적 세포 specific)
- 신생 표적 ADC (FOLR1 + EGFR + GPC3 + CDH6 + B7-H3 + LIV-1)
- payload 다양화 (DM1 + DM4 + MMAE + MMAF + DXd + camptothecin + PBD + duocarmycin + Bel(Bel))
- linker 다양화 (cleavable + non-cleavable + 미세조정)
- bystander effect + DAR (drug-antibody ratio)
- 한국 K-ADC + LegoChem + 셀트리온 ADC

