## 4. Phase plan (novel-drug-first)

- **Phase α (entry)**: roadmap stub + 20+ ADC drug list + 5-axis matrix.
- **Phase β**: hxq-adc-bystand-001 (next-gen ADC with optimized DAR + bystander effect + linker hybrid) build + VQE.
- **Phase γ**: antibody Fab + linker stability + payload release kinetics VQE (Enhertu T-DXd comparator).
- **Phase δ**: 20-ADC library ranking (HER2 + TROP2 + nectin-4 + CD33 + BCMA + FOLR1 heterogeneous payload).
- **Phase ε**: cross-axis pilot — top-ranked + WEAVE linker scaffold + NANOBOT bystander cell-penetration.

## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **gemtuzumab ozogamicin Mylotarg 2000** = first FDA ADC. 2010 withdrawal (early survival signal) → 2017 re-approval (lower-dose fractionated). first generation calicheamicin-CD33 AML — ADC modality 의 founding paradigm. cross-bone_marrow_failure.
2. **trastuzumab deruxtecan Enhertu T-DXd 2019** = paradigm shift. DXd payload + cleavable linker + DAR 8 + bystander effect → HER2-low (2022) + HER2-ultralow (2024) + lung (2024) expansion. DESTINY trial series 가 ADC era 정의.
3. **sacituzumab govitecan Trodelvy 2020** = first FDA TROP2 ADC. SN-38 (camptothecin-class) payload + breast TNBC + bladder. TROP2 epithelial broad expression이 selectivity 우려 → bystander 활용.
4. **enfortumab vedotin Padcev 2019** = first FDA nectin-4 ADC + 2023 1L urothelial 확장 (with pembrolizumab). MMAE-vedotin scaffold 반복 검증.
5. **belantamab mafodotin Blenrep 2020 → 2022 withdrawal → 2024-25 returns** = withdrawal-then-return rare pattern. DREAMM-7/-8 confirmatory trial이 efficacy 회복. BCMA ADC vs BCMA CAR-T vs BCMA bispecific 3-modality 경쟁.
6. **payload class diversification** — maytansinoid (DM1 Kadcyla / DM4 Elahere) + auristatin (MMAE Adcetris/Padcev/Polivy/Tivdak / MMAF Blenrep) + camptothecin (DXd Enhertu / SN-38 Trodelvy) + PBD (Zynlonta) + calicheamicin (Mylotarg/Besponsa) + duocarmycin + Bel — 5+ class combinatorial space.
7. **linker class diversification** — hydrazone (Mylotarg pH-sensitive) + thioether (Kadcyla non-cleavable) + valine-citrulline (Adcetris cathepsin-cleavable) + tetrapeptide-based (Enhertu cleavable) — release kinetics 가 efficacy + safety 결정.
8. **K-ADC industry** — LegoChem Biosciences ConjuAll platform (LCB14-0110, LCB84) 가 글로벌 deal $1B+ (J&J 2023, etc) 체결. 셀트리온 ADC + 한미약품 ADC pipeline. 한국 K-pharma 글로벌 modality leadership.
9. **bystander effect Enhertu** — DXd payload 가 tumor cell killing 후 외부 cell 침투 + heterogeneous tumor (HER2-low + ultralow) coverage. modality-paradigm-shifting feature.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, ADC modality 임상 의미 한정. Fab + linker + payload 결합만 modeling 가능.

